content.rendered:
Directed by Karan Vishwanath Kashyap

Written by Karan Vishwanath Kashyap

Cast Akshaye Khanna (Baba Bhandari). Priyaank Sharma (Pappu Mishra (as Priyank Sharma)). Riva Kishan (Mandira Shukla). Kaushik Satish (Mishraji). Satish Kaushik (Mishraji). Supriya Pathak (Emarti Devi). Rakesh Bedi (Kamta Prasad). Mrunal Jain (Vishnu). Swati Semwal (Urmila Shukla). Jaya Ojha (Mandira’s mother). Sunita Shirole (Mandira’s Dadi). Yuvika Chaudhary (Neelam). Ishtiyak Khan (Sonu Bullet). Apurva Nemlekar (Shyam). Shriya Saran (Dancer in the song ‘Naya Naya Love’). Nalneesh Neel (Haricharan). Mukesh S. Bhatt (Inspector (as Mukesh Bhatt)). Aditya Tiwari (Raghav). Manish Choudhary (Cricket Umpire). Mohammad Nayem (Mohammad Nayem). Sameer Patra (Milk man). Anand Sharma ((as Mrunal jain) (credit only))

Languages Hindi

Producers Prachi Manmohan

Production One Up Entertainment
